# Build
target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# IDE
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
*~

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Misc
*.log

# Local secrets / environment variables — never commit real credentials
# WHAT: .env files contain XAI_API_KEY (used by cabal-devmelopner --provider xai) and future provider keys (Claude, ADK, etc.).
# WHY: Prevents leaking secrets into git history. Required for 1.0 hardened release criteria and security-mcp scans. Complements git-secrets hook.
# WHY NOT: .env.example / .env.template are explicitly allowed for contributor setup.
# Setup: See AGENTS.md for git-secrets --install + patterns. Run `git secrets --scan` in hygiene.
# =============================================================================
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
.envrc
*.env
!.env.example
!.env.template
!.env.sample
*.key
secrets/
